## 7. Raster Analytics

### Funciones Raster (Raster Functions):

| Categoría | Funciones |
|-----------|-----------|
| **Índices** | NDVI, NDWI, SAVI, EVI, NDBI, BAI |
| **Clasificación** | Classify, Random Trees, SVM, Maximum Likelihood |
| **Álgebra** | Band Arithmetic, Raster Calculator |
| **Superficie** | Slope, Aspect, Hillshade, Curvature, Viewshed |
| **Hidrología** | Flow Direction, Flow Accumulation, Watershed |
| **Estadísticas** | Zonal Statistics, Cell Statistics, Focal Statistics |
| **Conversión** | Reclassify, Lookup, Raster to Polygon |
| **Filtros** | Convolution, Statistics, Focal |
| **Geometric** | Clip, Resample, Project, Mosaic |
| **Temporal** | Multidimensional Analysis, Trend, Anomaly |

### Uso desde Python:
```python
from arcgis.raster import ImageryLayer
from arcgis.raster.functions import ndvi, slope, aspect, hillshade

# NDVI
imagery = ImageryLayer("https://services.arcgis.com/.../ImageServer")
ndvi_result = ndvi(imagery, band_indexes="5 4")  # NIR, Red

# Slope
dem = ImageryLayer("https://elevation.arcgis.com/.../ImageServer")
slope_result = slope(dem, z_factor=1)

# Raster analytics distribuido (Image Server)
from arcgis.raster.analytics import generate_raster, calculate_density
result = generate_raster(raster_function=my_function, output_name="Analysis Result")
```

